title: Louisa and Jacob’s wedding
text:
Saturday 5th of September, 2026



Our wedding is on the 5th of September, 2026 in Copenhagen. We will also have some stuff going on the day before and the day after the wedding. The party will be at Nordhus, but see the program for more information. We would love to see you, and you can reply using the RSVP!
We will keep this website updated with details and upload photos afterwards.
